commit.message:
Drop end-of-life Django versions, add Django 2.2 and 3.0, and Python 3.8 (#108)

* Drop end-of-life Django versions, add Django 2.2 and 3.0, and Python 3.8

* Fix Django 4.0 DeprecationWarning

* Bump pytest dependencies

* Pin pytest at version compatible with Python 2.7 and don't try to run Django 3.0 on Python 3.5

* Don't test DRF < 3.10 on Django 3.0

* Drop end of life Python 2.7 and end of life Django 1.11

* Remove Django 2.1 trove classifier

* Bump pytest version now that Python 2.7 has been dropped

* Make test Model migrations

* Commit migrations

* Drop DRF 3.7 released in 2017

* Consolidate settings into a single location
